Text: Your FREE December Picture Prints from Sony ImageStationmcuilla We are pleased to send you another coupon for FREE highquality x prints from ImageStation redeemable anytime during the month of December INSTRUCTIONS AND COUPON CODE BELOW For questions regarding the free prints offer please see Get a jump on your holiday shopping with off framed prints at ImageStationcom Purchase any frame from now until Dec th and well automatically give you off the purchase price at checkout And when you choose any frame from our large selection of sizes and styles the print and giftwrapping is FREE Delight your friends and family with a custom framed photo that will brighten their mantel or desktop yearround To take advantage of this and other special holiday shopping before its too late go to zstz Thank you for making ImageStation your home for sharing pictures and video online Regards Your Friends at ImageStation YOUR DECEMBER COUPON CODE ISNJ To redeem your coupon First you need to upload your pictures to ImageStation Click the upload images link on the Welcome page to do this Next you need to move your images from your Inbox into an album To do this click on the Create Albums tab at the top of the page and follow instructions Once you have created your album click on the Order Prints link at the top of the page Click the Continue button at the bottom of the Prints page See the site for additional details about completing your order Enter your custom Coupon Code in the box on the Shopping Cart page and hit submit Thats it When you complete your transaction your Discount will be deducted from your final print total There will be a charge for shipping and handling Coupon Expires December Quality prints by Ofoto Ranked in print quality in a recent InfoTrends Research Group study ImageStation is a service mark of Sony Electronics Inc Ofoto is a trademark of Ofoto Inc c Sony Electronics Inc All Rights Reserved
